      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, garage-kept, and pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
