    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This AP2 chassis represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the high-revving F22C1 inline-four, this unit features a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline and VTEC engagement that remains sharp and visceral. The longitudinal drivetrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission, delivering power through a Torsen limited-slip differential. Every panel retains its original VIN tag, and the double-wishbone suspension remains tight with zero bushing degradation. This is a collector-grade example with flawless paint depth and a pristine undercarriage, offering a pure mechanical connection and unrivaled torsional rigidity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
